### Data Flow (Chat Analysis Pipeline)

The core pipeline is a **4.5-phase generator** in `_run_analysis_pipeline()`:

| Phase | What Happens | LLM Calls |
|-------|-------------|-----------|
| **0. Cache check** | LRU cache lookup (`filename:message`) | 0 |
| **0.5. Extraction** | Generate + execute code to extract categorical value distributions | 1 |
| **1. Code Generation** | Generate Pandas analysis code using full schema + extracted data + profile | 1 |
| **1.5. Execution + Retry** | Execute in AST-validated sandbox; retry up to 2× on failure | 0-2 |
| **2. Interpretation** | Send raw results back to Gemini for natural language explanation | 1 |
| **Fallback** | If all code paths fail, use text-only analysis (no code execution) | 1 |

**Per successful query**: 3 LLM calls minimum, up to 5 on retries. This is a notable cost consideration.

